title: HP OfficeJet Pro 9015e All-in-One Printer - High-Speed, High-Quality Printing
description: The HP OfficeJet Pro 9015e All-in-One Printer is designed for high-speed, high-quality printing in a professional office environment. With a print resolution of up to 4800 x 1200 dpi, it delivers crisp, vibrant documents and images. This all-in-one printer offers versatile functions including printing, scanning, copying, and faxing, catering to all your office needs. It prints up to 22 pages per minute in black and up to 20 pages per minute in color, making it an efficient choice for busy offices. The 250-sheet paper tray and 35-sheet automatic document feeder enhance productivity, while the wireless printing options such as HP Smart App and Apple AirPrint provide convenience and flexibility. The 2.65-inch color touchscreen allows for easy navigation and control of printer functions. The HP OfficeJet Pro 9015e combines speed, efficiency, and quality for a top-notch office printing experience.

title: HP OfficeJet Pro 9015e All-in-One Printer - Efficient and Versatile Office Solution
description: The HP OfficeJet Pro 9015e All-in-One Printer is the perfect solution for efficient and versatile office printing. It supports high-resolution printing up to 4800 x 1200 dpi, ensuring professional-quality documents. With fast print speeds of up to 22 pages per minute for black-and-white prints and 20 pages per minute for color prints, it meets the demands of a busy office. This model includes a 250-sheet paper tray, a 100-sheet output tray, and a 35-sheet automatic document feeder for seamless handling of large print jobs. The printer offers advanced features like wireless connectivity through HP Smart App and Apple AirPrint, and a user-friendly 2.65-inch color touchscreen. Ideal for all your office needs, the HP OfficeJet Pro 9015e combines performance, efficiency, and quality in one sleek package.
